title: Dance Laury Dance Discography VBR
description:
Dance Laury Dance is a rock metal band native of Quebec was founded in 2007. This is their collection, minus their self released CD-R "Out With Rockers" from 2009, which was mainly a demo version of 2011's "Living For The Roll". It's not included as it's now tricky to find and could only be gotten from live shows leading up to 2011. I'll still attempt to track down a copy to update the discography. In the meanwhile, enjoy some wicked tunes, grab a couple beers and relax!


(2011) Living For The Roll (CD)
(2014) Hellalujah (CD)


PLEASE, if you like ANY of this music, support the artist & go out to buy the fucking album(s), see the bands in concert, buy their t-shirts, etc... I'm certain they'll gladly appreciate it, as it costs them money to record, to travel to perform, etc. and have bills to pay like everyone else.
